{"tid":2273913,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地《海警法》草案列明海警可對不服從指令外國船動武","createTime":"2020-11-06T05:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T05:43:37.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"57871d00ca715ba8d64d36ac7a1106bfe04af741","tid":2273913,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:40:37.000Z","msg":"全國人大常委會公布《海警法》草案全文，第43條列明，如果外國船舶進入中國管轄海域非法從事生產作業活動、不服從停船指令或拒絕中國海警登船檢查，在警告無效後，海警人員可以使用武器。<br />\n<br />\n日本傳媒關注，在釣魚島、即日本稱為尖閣諸島附近作業的日本漁船，可能會成為目標。日本內閣官房長官加藤勝信說，高度關注中國海警的動向。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558536-20201105.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558536-20201105.htm&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8hZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=b8d753db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558536-20201105.htm&h=19a1aa6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558536-20201105.htm</a>"},{"pid":"76847791fe3bebf76916cc1781e9dad5eede8707","tid":2273913,"uid":11663,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:43:37.000Z","msg":"南海果啲係軍隊 唔係海警<br />\n所以唔用得武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}